20 NEW SECTION. Section 1. Big sky rail account. (1) There is a big sky rail account in the state
21 special revenue fund established in 17-2-102. The account consists of money deposited in the account
22 pursuant to 15-23-215 transferred into the account.
23 (2) The money in the account is statutorily appropriated, as provided in 17-7-502, to the
24 department of transportation.
25 (3) The department of transportation shall annually distribute by August 1 money in the account to
26 regional rail authorities established pursuant to 7-14-1621 before January 1, 2025. A regional rail authority shall
27 use the money for the purposes provided for in 7-14-1624(2).
